BT /F2 14 Tf 54 712.0 Td (Introduction) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 690.0 Td (High blood pressure \(hypertension\) is called the 'silent killer' because it often has no) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 676.0 Td (symptoms while damaging your heart, kidneys, brain, and blood vessels. The good news:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 662.0 Td (lifestyle changes can significantly reduce blood pressure, often by 10-20 points or more.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 638.2 Td (This workbook gives you the tools to monitor, manage, and reduce your blood pressure) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 624.2 Td (through the proven DASH diet, stress management, exercise, and daily tracking.) Tj ET
endstream
endobj
